                    <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303453</guid>
                    <description>
                        <![CDATA[<p>小米在早前的西班牙巴塞隆那發佈會，除了發佈小米 15 Ultra 外，耳機方面亦發佈了全新的 Buds 5 Pro 及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi，當中最特別就肯定是後者，畢竟它是市場上首款採用 Wi-Fi 連線與手機連結的耳機，理論上可為耳機帶來更廣頻寬，令用家可以用真無線耳機亦可聽到高質無損音樂。但事實是否如此？就讓試用了一段時間的 Edward 為大家實測一下吧。</p><h2>小米 Buds 5 Pro / Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi 開箱直擊</h2><p>在為大家分享這兩款小米全新真無線耳機的表現前，先讓 Edward 為大家帶來它們的開箱直擊吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01849-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01849-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01849.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303460" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02253-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02253-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02253.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這兩款就是小米最新推出的 Buds 5 Pro（上）及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（下）真無線耳機，現在就讓 Edward 為大家開箱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303461" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01856-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01856-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01856.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303462" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02255-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02255-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02255.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲從盒面大家已可看出兩者的分別，Wi-Fi 版盒面會印有 Wi-Fi 一字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01868-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01868-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01868.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02263-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02263-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02263.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲兩隻耳機一打開盒就已經會見到耳機盒真身，耳機就收藏在充電盒內。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303465" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01871-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01871-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01871.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02266-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02266-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02266.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而兩隻耳機底層均見到説明書，其他配件就收藏在頂部及底部的夾層。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01873-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01873-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01873.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02267-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02267-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02267.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲兩款耳機均會附送 USB-A to USB-C 充電線，以及另外三個不同大細的耳塞（XS、S 及 L），而已裝在耳機的就是 M 碼。至此兩款耳機開箱已完成。</p><h2>設計小不同但類近</h2><p>今次小米發佈的兩款全新真無線耳機 Buds 5 Pro（下文簡稱 B5P）及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（下文簡稱 B5P Wi-Fi），其實兩者均是屬於 Buds 5 系列，所以在設計語言上兩隻新耳機均頗為相近，唯一較大分別是 B5P Wi-Fi 採用半透明充電盒，而且充電盒內邊位兩處位置印有紅色標記；而 B5P 就採用了鏡面設計的充電盒，盒內亦沒有相關紅色標記而已。這兩個位就是分辨是否 Wi-Fi 版本的方法，其他無論是大細、重量、按鍵 / 插槽位置，兩者均是相同的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303470" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01882-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01882-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01882.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02276-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02276-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02276.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小米 Buds 5 Pro（上）及 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（下）畢竟屬於同一系列，所以設計十分相近，最明顯分別就是充電盒方面，前者採用鏡面設計，而後者就採用半透式設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02279-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02279-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02279.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而打開充電盒，就會見到 Buds 5 Pro Wi-Fi（右）的盒蓋及右耳機充電位旁均有一個紅色標記，但 Buds 5 Pro（左）的充電盒就沒有這個設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02285-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02285-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc02285.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，兩款耳機機身均採用啞面平實設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303473" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01908-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01908-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc01908.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而兩款耳機的耳柄均加入了拋光設計，還算有一定的層次感。</p><br /><b>
]]>
                    </description>
